[raw_stderr] python -m venv .venv
[raw_stderr] ```
[raw_stderr] 
[raw_stderr] Windows PowerShell:
[raw_stderr] 
[raw_stderr] ```powershell
[raw_stderr] .\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
[raw_stderr] ```
[raw_stderr] 
[raw_stderr] macOS oder Linux:
